Recover action dice # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_1_military_2

===phase_1_military_2===
Draw Event and Faction Event cards # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_1_military_3

===phase_1_military_3===
More than 6 Event cards in hand? # CLASS: w3-yellow
+ [Yes] -> phase_1_military_discard
+ [No] -> phase_2_military 
TODO: Implement Warriors of Middle Earth

===phase_1_military_discard===
Event card discard priority: # CLASS: w3-yellow
1. Doesn't use the term "Fellowship Revealed" # CLASS: w3-yellow
2. Character card # CLASS: w3-yellow
3. Strategy card # CLASS: w3-yellow
4. Descending order of priority # CLASS: w3-yellow
5. Doesn't place a tile # CLASS: w3-yellow
+ [Done] -> phase_2_military

===phase_2_military===
<b>Phase 2</b> # CLASS: w3-green
Shadow victory points lower than Corruption points? # CLASS: w3-yellow
+ [Yes] -> phase_3_corruption # IMAGE: corruption_strategy.jpg

+ [No] -> phase_3_military

===phase_3_military===
<b>Phase 3</b> # CLASS: w3-green
Select first Fellowship state, starting from top: # CLASS: w3-yellow
+ Fellowship on the Mordor track # CLASS: w3-yellow
 -> phase_3_military_max
+ Fellowship progress is greater than 5 # CLASS: w3-yellow
 -> phase_3_military_2
+ Fellowship in starting location and progress is 0 # CLASS: w3-yellow
 -> phase_3_military_0
+ None of the above # CLASS: w3-yellow
 -> phase_3_military_1

===phase_3_military_max===
Assign maximum dice allowed to the hunt pool # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_4_military

===phase_3_military_0===
Assign 0 dice to the hunt pool # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_4_military

===phase_3_military_1===
Assign 1 die to the hunt pool # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_4_military

===phase_3_military_2===
Assign 2 dice to the hunt pool # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_4_military

===phase_4_military===
<b>Phase 4</b> # CLASS: w3-green
Roll remaining action dice # CLASS: w3-orange
+ [Done] -> phase_5_military